      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable daily driver that\u2019s full of character! This car is a solid runner that will get you where you need to go reliably. While it shows its age with some clear cosmetic wear on the body and interior, it remains a functional and honest vehicle perfect for someone looking for value and utility.",
