    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and shows clear signs of its age and regular use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dings on the passenger side doors. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear, and there are some stains on the rear floor mats. Mechanically, it remains reliable for daily commuting, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional car at a budget-friendly price point.",
