    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and shows clear signs of age and regular use. While it remains mechanically operational, the exterior has several noticeable scratches, a small dent on the rear passenger door, and some fading on the clear coat. Inside, the upholstery is worn with some staining on the carpets, and the air conditioning is not as cold as it once was. This car is a functional daily driver that would benefit from some cosmetic and minor mechanical attention.",
